<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1158</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ jī kě de shí hòu, yuàn gěi nǐ sòng yī bēi shuǐ.
 nǐ yōu chóu de shí hòu, yuàn gěi nǐ sòng qù ān wèi.
 yǒu zhòng dān de shí hòu, yuàn gěi nǐ yī qǐ fēn dān.
 nǐ kū qì de shí hòu, yuàn péi nǐ yī qǐ liú lèi.
 zhè shì xiōng dì jiě mèi duì nǐ de chéng nuò,
 yuàn yì jǐn xīn jǐn lì fú shì zhǔ gěi de měi yī cì jī huì.
 shēn shēn qī pàn měi yī gè rén dōu dé dào shèng líng de huó shuǐ.
 rèn shì zhēn lǐ gāo jǔ zhēn lǐ, ēn huì yǒng xiāng suí.</lyrics>
<title>yuàn 迦南1158</title>
</song>